profile:
Accurate Window Cleaners started in 1970 with a focus on strong work ethic, family values and attention to detail. Over the years and through the generations, we have remained committed to our Dutch roots and ensuring the traditions of high quality work and friendly customer service. Our aim is your peace of mind and to provide a window cleaning service that exceeds our clients expectations.

Now into our third generation of a father and son partnership, owners Jack and Matt oversee each step of the process from the initial customer contact and convenient scheduling, to the window cleaning itself. This includes careful inspection of any employee work to ensure every window meets our high quality standards.

We recognize the importance and value of community and are proud to support various local veteranâ€™s clubs, non-profit, sports and health organizations through fundraising and volunteer initiatives.
